                    <section class="cc-studio-hero">
                        <div class="cc-page-shell">
                            <span class="cc-page-badge">Showroom Experience</span>
                            <h1 class="cc-page-title">A studio-led presentation for clients who want the room to feel resolved, not improvised.</h1>
                            <p class="cc-page-copy">The Craik &amp; Comfort approach frames bathroom products through mood, scale, finish, and compatibility, helping shoppers move faster from inspiration to confident specification.</p>
                        </div>
                    </section>

                    <section class="cc-studio-section">
                        <div class="cc-page-shell">
                            <div class="cc-studio-grid">
                                <div class="cc-studio-body">
                                    <h2>From product browsing to a more complete bathroom conversation.</h2>
                                    <p>This page introduces the studio feel behind the website. Instead of relying on a generic eCommerce presentation, the new direction brings in more editorial hierarchy, stronger visual cues, and clearer pathways for homeowners and trade clients.</p>
                                    <p>The result is a site that feels closer to a premium design destination while still supporting real shopping, enquiries, and day-to-day product discovery.</p>
                                    <div class="cc-studio-metrics">
                                        <div class="cc-studio-metric">
                                            <strong>6</strong>
                                            <span>Core product groups arranged to support easier project planning.</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="cc-studio-metric">
                                            <strong>1</strong>
                                            <span>Consistent visual language built around charcoal, soft stone gray, and terracotta red.</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="cc-studio-metric">
                                            <strong>24h</strong>
                                            <span>Fast-response enquiry positioning for consultation and support flows.</span>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="cc-studio-card">
